@meta
title: Payment Incident Runbook
version: 0.1
owner: sre-pay

@map
- RUN-001 | Detection Conditions | Define alert thresholds and detection signals
- RUN-010 | Severity Classification | Define severity levels by user impact
- RUN-020 | Immediate Actions | Define first-10-minute stabilization steps
- RUN-030 | Communication | Define internal and external update protocol
- RUN-040 | Exit Criteria | Define incident closure conditions

@section RUN-001
title: Detection Conditions
summary: Combine failure and latency signals for reliable incident detection
links: ALERT-001
content:
<<<
[Signal thresholds]
1) Failure rate:
2) Latency P95:
3) Timeout count:

